<p>
 
</p>
<ul><li><a class="wiki" href="/wiki/TestEnvRequirements">TestEnvRequirements</a> - requirements for test environment for BIND10 DNS and DHCP, that could also be reused for ISC DHCP4 and BIND9.
</li><li><a class="wiki" href="/wiki/DhcpValidation">DhcpValidation</a> - our plans for DHCP validation (including Kea and ISC DHCP4).
</li></ul><h2 id="Notes">Notes</h2>
